Class NativeGraphRepositoryInformation

java.lang.Object
  com.fluidops.fedx.provider.RepositoryInformation
      com.fluidops.fedx.provider.NativeGraphRepositoryInformation

public class NativeGraphRepositoryInformation
extends RepositoryInformation

Graph information for Sesame NativeStore initialization.

Format:

<%name%> fluid:store "NativeStore"; fluid:RepositoryLocation "%location%". relative path (to Config.getBaseDir()) fluid:store "NativeStore"; fluid:RepositoryLocation "data\\repositories\\native-storage.dbpedia". absolute Path fluid:store "NativeStore"; fluid:RepositoryLocation "D:\\data\\repositories\\native-storage.dbpedia". Note: the id is constructed from the location: repositories\\native-storage.dbpedia => native-storage.dbpedia

Author:
Andreas Schwarte
